# Automation God-Package Shim-First Decomposition

(v1.0.0 body documented the PROPOSED, unexecuted 52-file SPLIT of hephaestus/automation/
into 8 domain sub-packages: Step 0 pre-flight checks for __all__, pytest import mode,
circular-import audit, shared-ownership and re-export-name verification; Steps 1-9 for the
move-and-shim workflow; a 7-row "Unverified Assumptions" table; an N/A Failed Attempts
placeholder; scale params for issue #1177; and Explicit/Wildcard shim templates. The
Explicit shim templates carried `# ruff: noqa: F401`, which v2.0.0 corrects. Outcome was
"Plan written for issue #1177; NOT YET EXECUTED".)
